變～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定會有更好既人等緊你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你女仔怕咩 仲會有人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>男人最痛.....</blockquote>我怕啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呢啲性格好難識到新朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n內向又靜又怕醜...個樣又一般...可能因為咁我ex從來都唔驚我會帽佢...<br />\n最近試過同人曖昧左半個月,出黎食餐飯都冇乜幾句,多數都係佢同我朋友傾計...第二日就冇左下聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但其實識得耐左我就系另一個人黎...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 2點訓 7點起左身....女仔易治癒過男既 男要起返身 唔易<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c93f9527d28be247d50fdb6566b85ead41adedf","tid":583884,"uid":32859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T23:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我.....隔左一星期再用其他方法搵佢...終於知道...佢前任搵返佢..先至對我咁決絕....我...呢世人比人帽左第三次...點解每個女仔都會係咁... 聽日佢生日...我上個月已經調埋假陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我一心諗住同你結婚...我無介意過你身份...<br />\n點解每次比人帽都係我...世上係咪唔會有好既女仔？<br />\n我好痛苦 好想搵人比我叫春....</blockquote>日日都綠帽 都慣有咩所謂</blockquote><br />\n真係無論你管得嚴定唔嚴 要帽你就帽你"},{"pid":"b95ca0910606c94fcebdc19b837c8e244dbf7753","tid":583884,"uid":32859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T23:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度成班垃圾[img]assets/faces/lihkg/dog1.gif[/img] [img]assets/faces/lihkg/dog2.gif[/img]<br />\n80歲都唔好比飽飯d女食就岩架啦<br />\n日日屌到佢地嗌救命啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你啱"},{"pid":"6335bec62d935eb7c117b154e53c0f8ef8a1d9c5","tid":583884,"uid":96528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T23:46:23.000Z","msg":"唔係有第二個唔會咁絕情"},{"pid":"8bdae488cd672c27e89ad92450d10378ef058e62","tid":583884,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T23